OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FZoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,8,FMorris has been remembered for his
OL,9,F"lifetime of exploration, curiosity
OL,10,Fand creativity" after his death aged
OL,11,F98 on Sunday.
OL,13,FThe TV star, who hosted the popular
OL,14,Fshow Zoo Time, rose to fame in 1967
OL,15,Fwhen his book The Naked Ape became an
OL,16,Finternational bestseller.
OL,18,FHis son Jason said: "His was a
OL,19,Flifetime of exploration, curiosity and
OL,20,Fcreativity.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@OO]zD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
