CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,F"A zoologist, manwatcher, author and
OL,8,Fartist, he was still writing and
OL,9,Fpainting right up until his death.
OL,11,F"He was a great man and an even better
OL,12,Ffather and grandfather."
OL,14,FThe Wiltshire-born author joined the
OL,15,FBritish Army in 1946 and fulfilled two
OL,16,Fyears of national service before later
OL,17,Fpursuing his interest in the arts and
OL,18,Fstudying natural history.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
