PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FHe became the face of ITV Granada's
OL,8,Fhit nature series Zoo Time in 1956,
OL,9,Fwhich ran from 1956 until 1967 and
OL,10,Ffeatured animal experts and zoo staff
OL,11,Fand explored the behaviour of animals.
OL,13,FMorris also hosted many art
OL,14,Fexhibitions throughout his career,
OL,15,Fincluding one at the Institute of
OL,16,FContemporary Arts in London in 1957,
OL,17,Fwhich combined his interests in
OL,18,Fanimals and painting, showcasing a
OL,19,Fseries of works created by chimpanzees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
