PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FHe also co-organised an exhibition
OL,8,Ftitled The Lost Image in 1958, which
OL,9,Fcompared images created by infants,
OL,10,Fhuman adults and apes and was on
OL,11,Fdisplay at the Royal Festival Hall in
OL,12,FLondon.
OL,14,FMorris became the Zoological Society's
OL,15,Fcurator of mammals at London Zoo in
OL,16,F1959, a post he held for eight years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
