PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FHe started his career with the BBC in
OL,8,F1965, hosting its Life In The Animal
OL,9,FWorld programme, and later went on to
OL,10,Fheadline many documentaries for the
OL,11,Fcorporation.
OL,13,FIn 1967, Morris penned his most
OL,14,Fpopular book, The Naked Ape: A
OL,15,FZoologist's Study Of The Human Animal,
OL,16,Fwhich led to his global recognition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
