PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FFollowing its success, he wrote many
OL,8,Ffollow-up books, including The Human
OL,9,FZoo (1969), Manwatching (1977) and The
OL,10,FNaked Man (1977), and has contributed
OL,11,Fto more than 90 titles in his decades-
OL,12,Flong career dedicated to the study of
OL,13,Fanimals and zoology.
OL,15,FDuring his tenure as a broadcaster, he
OL,16,Fhosted BBC documentaries including
OL,17,FManwatching (1977), TV And Natural
OL,18,FHistory (1986) and The Human Animal
OL,19,F(1994), and he had regular appearances
OL,20,Fon shows such as The Animals Roadshow
OL,21,Fand Friday Night And Saturday Morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
