PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776704797
OL,3,C'A great man': Tributes paid to
OL,4,Czoologist and TV presenter Desmond
OL,5,CMorris
OL,7,FIn recent years, Morris continued to
OL,8,Fdedicate his life to his academic
OL,9,Fendeavours and his work as a
OL,10,Fsurrealist artist, having held many
OL,11,Fexhibitions showcasing his work.
OL,13,FThe BBC also released a programme
OL,14,Ftitled The Secret Surrealist in 2017,
OL,15,Fshowcasing Morris and his artwork as
OL,16,Fit examined his "double life" as a
OL,17,Fpainter.
